window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sacrificing his life to protect his best friend was a decision Hui Yue did not regret.</b></p> <p>Yet who could have known that death was not the final destination, but rather the beginning of a new adventure into a world filled with demonic beasts and martial arts cultivation? Hui Yue soon finds that within this world, strength is what determined your future accomplishments...and there is no space for the weak. Embarking upon this new life, Hui Yue meets friends, experiences betrayal, and embarks on his own journey of cultivation to overcome his limits and increase his strength.</p>"; 
